Dia lalai kerana
tonton drama Korea Selatan.

238
00:14:40,411 --> 00:14:41,579
Kapten awak pula…

239
00:14:42,413 --> 00:14:44,082
Akan direvolusikan?

240
00:14:44,207 --> 00:14:46,087
DIREVOLUSIKAN:
DIPECAT DAN DIJADIKAN BURUH PAKSA

241
00:14:46,111 --> 00:14:48,753
Awak pula, si kucing licik!
Minum waktu bertugas?

242
00:14:48,836 --> 00:14:49,879
Awak paling teruk.

243
00:14:52,423 --> 00:14:53,549
Kapten Ri,

244
00:14:54,175 --> 00:14:56,511
mana dia tahu semua itu?

245
00:14:57,136 --> 00:14:58,554
Awak rasa?

246
00:15:11,317 --> 00:15:12,485
Helo.

247
00:15:12,693 --> 00:15:15,363
Dah dengar berita baik itu?

248
00:15:15,446 --> 00:15:16,906
Di Gunung Suseok, ada wanita…

249
00:15:16,989 --> 00:15:17,990
Bukan.

250
00:15:18,074 --> 00:15:20,076
- Wanita tak dikenali…
- Bukan.

251
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:21,577
Tentu awaklah Eun Dong.

252
00:15:22,161 --> 00:15:23,788
Maaf? Awak…

253
00:15:24,247 --> 00:15:27,458
Saya dengar,
awak akan dibuang daripada perkhidmatan.

254
00:15:27,542 --> 00:15:29,210
Maksudnya, dipecat.

255
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:31,838
Awak perlukan kerja ini, bukan?

256
00:15:34,757 --> 00:15:35,883
Dia belum mati?

257
00:15:35,967 --> 00:15:37,218
Belum.

258
00:15:38,678 --> 00:15:39,929
Awaklah Ju Meok?

259
00:15:40,805 --> 00:15:42,765
Garangnya nama. "Buku Lima"?

260
00:15:42,849 --> 00:15:44,225
Sesuai untuk askar.

261
00:15:45,184 --> 00:15:48,729
Drama Korea Selatan mana satu
yang awak tonton hingga lalai?

262
00:15:49,290 --> 00:15:50,290
<i>Stairway to Heaven</i>.

263
00:15:50,314 --> 00:15:52,525
Itu drama lama.

264
00:15:52,608 --> 00:15:54,443
Ada Ji-woo dan Sang-woo, bukan?

265
00:15:54,527 --> 00:15:55,611
Saya kawan mereka.

266
00:15:55,695 --> 00:15:57,780
Dulu, Ji-woo jiran saya.

267
00:15:57,864 --> 00:15:58,864
Betulkah?

268
00:16:00,032 --> 00:16:02,076
- Itu yang awak nak tahu?
- Maaf.

269
00:16:02,493 --> 00:16:04,912
Jangan tercegat di situ. Mari masuk.

270
00:16:04,996 --> 00:16:06,664
Mari duduk bersembang.

271
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,292
Kita ambil jalan mudah.

272
00:16:09,876 --> 00:16:12,461
Hantar saya ke tempat saya mendarat.

273
00:16:12,545 --> 00:16:14,046
Saya akan balik sendiri.

274
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:17,008
Cuaca hari ini cerah. Mudahlah.

275
00:16:17,633 --> 00:16:19,260
- Tak boleh.
- Kenapa?

276
00:16:19,343 --> 00:16:21,470
Kapten Ri, biarkan dia.

277
00:16:21,554 --> 00:16:25,057
Biar dia dipanggang pagar elektrik
hingga garing.

278
00:16:25,141 --> 00:16:28,352
Baru dia tahu bahaya pagar elektrik.

279
00:16:28,436 --> 00:16:29,770
Kalau tak, tak tahu.

280
00:16:32,356 --> 00:16:34,567
Semalam, pagar elektrik itu mati

281
00:16:34,650 --> 00:16:36,652
kerana generator dirosakkan angin.

282
00:16:36,736 --> 00:16:38,863
Tapi, ia dah dibaiki.

283
00:16:38,946 --> 00:16:41,157
Sebab itu saya suruh hantarkan.

284
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:43,492
Kamu askar. Ini kawasan kamu.

285
00:16:43,576 --> 00:16:46,704
Kami baru selesai bertugas
dua bulan di sempadan

286
00:16:46,787 --> 00:16:48,623
dan pulang ke unit pagi ini.

287
00:16:48,998 --> 00:16:51,209
Kami tak boleh kembali
buat beberapa bulan lagi.

288
00:16:51,751 --> 00:16:55,796
Jangan asyik kata tak boleh.

289
00:16:55,880 --> 00:16:58,257
Cubalah cari jalan.

290
00:16:58,341 --> 00:17:00,259
Tiada jalan lain.

291
00:17:00,343 --> 00:17:02,720
Paling mudah, tanam dia elok-elok.

292
00:17:02,803 --> 00:17:04,055
Saya tak tanya awak.

293
00:17:04,972 --> 00:17:07,850
Perempuan tak guna bermulut busuk.

294
00:17:07,934 --> 00:17:08,934
Apa?

295
00:17:09,727 --> 00:17:10,727
"Mulut busuk"?

296
00:17:11,062 --> 00:17:13,397
Itu cara orang di sini mencaci?

297
00:17:13,481 --> 00:17:15,566
Nak dengar cacian Korea Selatan?

298
00:17:16,317 --> 00:17:19,153
Cacian kami boleh tahan pedas!

299
00:17:19,237 --> 00:17:20,321
Cukup!

300
00:17:20,988 --> 00:17:24,325
Kamu nak bertanding caci-mencaci

301
00:17:24,825 --> 00:17:26,452
dalam situasi ini?

302
00:17:26,953 --> 00:17:28,996
Betul. Saya tak patut marah.

303
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,748
Kita bincang elok-elok.

304
00:17:31,832 --> 00:17:34,085
Jadi, ini

305
00:17:34,168 --> 00:17:36,629
kali pertama rakyat Korea Selatan

306
00:17:36,712 --> 00:17:38,381
mendarat di Korea Utara?

307
00:17:38,464 --> 00:17:40,967
Ada protokol untuk kes begini?

308
00:17:41,444 --> 00:17:42,444
Manual?

309
00:17:42,468 --> 00:17:44,679
Ikut manual, awak akan disoal siasat

310
00:17:44,762 --> 00:17:46,430
Jabatan Keselamatan Negara.

311
00:17:46,514 --> 00:17:49,225
Tak habis-habis dengan
Jabatan Keselamatan Negara.

312
00:17:49,308 --> 00:17:52,561
Itu macam polis atau NIS?

313
00:17:53,771 --> 00:17:54,814
Lebih kuranglah.

314
00:17:54,897 --> 00:17:58,317
Jadi, kenapa tak bawa saya ke sana

315
00:17:58,401 --> 00:18:00,152
waktu kita terserempak?

316
00:18:02,530 --> 00:18:06,158
Saya dah agak.
Kalau saya ceritakan kepada mereka,

317
00:18:07,201 --> 00:18:08,452
habislah kamu semua.

318
00:18:09,745 --> 00:18:10,830
Betul?

319
00:18:11,956 --> 00:18:15,710
Sebab itu saya nak minta tolong.

320
00:18:15,793 --> 00:18:18,921
Kamu tak mengaku, tapi
sebenarnya situasi kita sama.

321
00:18:22,133 --> 00:18:25,094
Ya, Stairway to Heaven,
beri pendapat.

322
00:18:25,177 --> 00:18:27,388
Ayah saya tekong.

323
00:18:28,514 --> 00:18:29,890
Apa? Tekong?

324
00:18:30,308 --> 00:18:31,308
Tekong.

325
00:18:31,684 --> 00:18:32,727
"Tekong"?

326
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:36,647
Ayah dia pandu bot
ke perairan antarabangsa.

327
00:18:37,148 --> 00:18:39,650
Bot kecil dipandu ke tengah laut

328
00:18:39,734 --> 00:18:43,029
untuk curi-curi berjumpa bot
yang hendak ke negara lain.

329
00:18:43,112 --> 00:18:45,823
Itu idea bagus.

330
00:18:46,324 --> 00:18:47,533
Tekong.

331
00:18:47,950 --> 00:18:51,495
Ju Meok, saya akan beri awak
autograf Ji-woo.

332
00:18:52,246 --> 00:18:53,706
Betul? Bila?

333
00:18:53,789 --> 00:18:55,499
Selepas Korea bersatu.

334
00:18:56,125 --> 00:18:59,337
Suatu hari nanti.
Jadi, bila kita boleh bertolak?

335
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:02,631
Ayah bertolak dari Pelabuhan Jinheung
setiap 15 hari.

336
00:19:02,715 --> 00:19:03,716
Tiga hari lagi.

337
00:19:03,799 --> 00:19:04,799
"Tiga hari"?

338
00:19:05,718 --> 00:19:07,386
Tak boleh lebih awal?

339
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:08,888
Kena tunggu tiga hari,

340
00:19:08,971 --> 00:19:12,641
kemudian kena rentas negara lain.

341
00:19:13,601 --> 00:19:17,271
Saya ada mesyuarat agung
dengan pemegang saham.

342
00:19:17,355 --> 00:19:18,898
- Hei.
- Mesyuarat ini

343
00:19:18,981 --> 00:19:20,399
amat penting bagi saya.

344
00:19:20,483 --> 00:19:23,194
Mesyuarat paling penting
dalam hidup saya.

345
00:19:23,277 --> 00:19:25,071
Dengar baik-baik.

346
00:19:26,197 --> 00:19:28,866
Awak punca semua ini berlaku.

347
00:19:28,949 --> 00:19:31,035
Awak yang salah pilih jalan pulang.

348
00:19:31,744 --> 00:19:34,663
Awak patut rasa bersalah
kerana menyusahkan orang.

349
00:19:37,041 --> 00:19:38,041
Betul.

350
00:19:39,168 --> 00:19:41,045
Saya minta maaf.

351
00:19:41,629 --> 00:19:43,381
Tentu kamu semua terkejut.

352
00:19:43,464 --> 00:19:44,590
Sekarang, pilih.

353
00:19:45,693 --> 00:19:46,693
Pilih apa?

354
00:19:46,717 --> 00:19:49,929
Saya boleh bawa awak
ke Jabatan Keselamatan Negara.

355
00:19:50,012 --> 00:19:51,889
- Kapten Ri.
- Itu agak…

356
00:19:51,972 --> 00:19:53,972
Selepas disoal siasat,
awak mungkin dihantar balik.

357
00:19:53,996 --> 00:19:55,768
Mungkin juga tidak.

358
00:19:55,893 --> 00:19:57,144
Saya tak boleh janji.

359
00:19:57,228 --> 00:19:59,146
Apa pilihan lain?

360
00:19:59,230 --> 00:20:00,648
Tadi, awak suruh pilih.

361
00:20:03,943 --> 00:20:05,486
Ikut arahan kami.

362
00:20:05,569 --> 00:20:08,030
Arahan apa?

363
00:20:08,114 --> 00:20:11,617
Pertama, jangan keluar dari rumah ini
selama awak di sini.

364
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:15,287
Saya tahulah. Saya tak gila.
Saya takkan ke mana-mana.

365
00:20:15,371 --> 00:20:18,040
Jangan bercakap dengan kami.

366
00:20:18,124 --> 00:20:19,792
Jangan sebar ideologi Selatan.

367
00:20:19,875 --> 00:20:22,670
Bagus. Jangan cakap dengan saya juga.

368
00:20:22,753 --> 00:20:25,172
Jangan cuba pengaruhi saya.
Takkan berjaya.

369
00:20:25,256 --> 00:20:29,260
Setelah pulang ke Selatan,
jangan dedah apa-apa yang berlaku di sini.

370
00:20:30,428 --> 00:20:32,763
Tak perlu risau tentang itu.

371
00:20:32,847 --> 00:20:34,473
Saya takkan beritahu orang.

372
00:20:34,557 --> 00:20:37,893
Saya akan terkena amnesia setelah pulang.

373
00:20:38,018 --> 00:20:40,813
Betul kata dia.

374
00:20:40,896 --> 00:20:44,817
Dalam drama Korea Selatan,
hampir semua orang menghidap amnesia.

375
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,361
Itu penyakit biasa di negara kapitalis.

376
00:20:47,445 --> 00:20:48,279
Betulkah?

377
00:20:48,362 --> 00:20:50,823
Sebab itu mereka suka
minum soda Amerika?

378
00:20:51,365 --> 00:20:53,617
Menarik.

379
00:20:53,701 --> 00:20:55,828
Baiklah, kalau begitu…

380
00:20:55,911 --> 00:20:59,331
Saya pun nak minta tolong.

381
00:20:59,415 --> 00:21:01,292
Perkara kecil saja.

382
00:21:01,375 --> 00:21:03,961
Saya makan daging dua kali sehari.

383
00:21:04,044 --> 00:21:05,129
Saya suka daging.

384
00:21:06,088 --> 00:21:08,215
Hei, perempuan Selatan.

385
00:21:08,299 --> 00:21:09,592
Jangan mengoceh!

386
00:21:10,134 --> 00:21:11,177
Mengoceh?

387
00:21:11,802 --> 00:21:13,762
Maksudnya, "Jangan mengarut"?

388
00:21:14,472 --> 00:21:17,600
"Jangan mengarut"?
Maksudnya, "Jangan mengoceh"?

389
00:21:18,017 --> 00:21:20,060
Ya, sama.

390
00:21:21,854 --> 00:21:22,897
Kapten Ri.

391
00:21:23,355 --> 00:21:26,942
Perempuan ini cuba memperdaya orang kita.

392
00:21:27,026 --> 00:21:29,945
Dia bercakap yang bukan-bukan

393
00:21:30,029 --> 00:21:33,199
dan sebar budaya
makan daging dua kali sehari!

394
00:21:33,282 --> 00:21:34,617
Terpulanglah.

395
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:37,161
Apa-apa pun, inilah saya,

396
00:21:37,244 --> 00:21:39,830
Awak pun tahu saya
sudah dua hari kelaparan.

397
00:21:39,914 --> 00:21:41,499
Saya dah berjalan jauh.

398
00:21:41,582 --> 00:21:44,835
Penglihatan saya dah mula kabur.

399
00:21:44,919 --> 00:21:48,839
Maaf, awak ada daging?

400
00:21:58,974 --> 00:22:01,644
Maaf, lama awak tunggu.

401
00:22:01,727 --> 00:22:03,020
Maafkan saya.

402
00:22:03,103 --> 00:22:05,231
Dah akhir tahun. Sibuk sedikit.

403
00:22:05,314 --> 00:22:07,983
Tak apa. Siapkanlah kerja dulu.

404
00:22:08,067 --> 00:22:08,901
Mana boleh?

405
00:22:08,984 --> 00:22:11,612
Awak lebih penting daripada kerja.

406
00:22:11,695 --> 00:22:14,490
Awak yang kenalkan saya
dengan bos awak.

407
00:22:17,243 --> 00:22:20,162
Sejak kontrak itu ditandatangani,

408
00:22:20,246 --> 00:22:22,248
saya dihormati di pejabat.

409
00:22:22,331 --> 00:22:25,709
Pengurus tak guna itu pun
tak berani kacau saya.

410
00:22:25,793 --> 00:22:27,670
Sekarang,

411
00:22:27,753 --> 00:22:29,964
saya sengaja cari fasal dengan dia.

412
00:22:30,047 --> 00:22:31,465
Tapi dia diam saja.

413
00:22:32,049 --> 00:22:33,050
Bodoh.

414
00:22:33,133 --> 00:22:35,177
Kenapa awak buat begitu?

415
00:22:35,261 --> 00:22:36,554
Jangan risau.

416
00:22:36,637 --> 00:22:39,932
- Sekarang, saya boleh.
- Tak boleh.

417
00:22:40,015 --> 00:22:43,269
Saya dah tak takut dibuang kerja.

418
00:22:43,352 --> 00:22:45,354
Su-chan, awak dah silap.

419
00:22:45,437 --> 00:22:49,275
Saya berjaya dapatkan kontrak
bernilai sepuluh bilion won.

420
00:22:49,358 --> 00:22:53,654
Chang-sik, nampaknya
saya akan dinaikkan pangkat.

421
00:22:54,321 --> 00:22:56,031
Bos saya dah hilang.

422
00:22:56,115 --> 00:22:57,575
Apa maksud awak?

423
00:22:57,658 --> 00:22:58,951
Dia mungkin dah mati.

424
00:22:59,618 --> 00:23:02,580
Sudah 24 jam dia diisytiharkan hilang.

425
00:23:02,663 --> 00:23:04,123
Jangan bergurau.

426
00:23:04,748 --> 00:23:05,791
Maaf.

427
00:23:06,458 --> 00:23:07,585
Saya serius.

428
00:23:08,210 --> 00:23:11,922
Kenapa awak sengaja
cari fasal dengan pengurus?

429
00:23:12,006 --> 00:23:12,840
Tak apalah.

430
00:23:12,923 --> 00:23:16,093
Saya tak patut kenalkan awak dengan dia.
Maaf.

431
00:23:21,432 --> 00:23:24,393
Tuhan, aku berdoa agar suamiku…

432
00:23:24,977 --> 00:23:27,563
Dijadikan pewaris syarikat

433
00:23:27,646 --> 00:23:32,067
seperti yang Kau takdirkan,
secepat mungkin.

434
00:23:32,151 --> 00:23:34,987
Limpahkanlah rahmat ke atasnya.

435
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,405
Semadikanlah…

436
00:23:36,488 --> 00:23:37,573
Tuhanku!

437
00:23:39,533 --> 00:23:40,576
Tidak.

438
00:23:41,076 --> 00:23:42,745
Ini tak mungkin terjadi.

439
00:23:43,078 --> 00:23:44,496
Ini mustahil.

440
00:23:44,705 --> 00:23:47,458
Kembalikanlah wanita itu dengan selamat.

441
00:23:48,292 --> 00:23:50,419
Jagalah dia daripada bahaya.

442
00:23:50,502 --> 00:23:53,672
Janganlah Kau ambil nyawanya.

443
00:23:53,756 --> 00:23:56,050
Bawalah dia pulang.

444
00:23:56,508 --> 00:23:58,052
- Tuhanku…
- Tuhan.

445
00:23:58,260 --> 00:23:59,928
Tuhan, saya tak mahu begitu.

446
00:24:00,012 --> 00:24:00,929
Tuhan.

447
00:24:01,013 --> 00:24:02,013
Makbulkan doaku!

448
00:24:02,056 --> 00:24:04,016
- Sebelahi aku.
- Tuhan…

449
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:17,738
PEMIMPIN SENTIASA BERSAMA KITA

450
00:24:54,942 --> 00:24:56,860
Tahun ini, kubis tak banyak.

451
00:24:56,944 --> 00:24:58,696
- Betul.
- Tapi manis.

452
00:24:58,779 --> 00:25:02,825
Cuma dua tan untuk lima keluarga.
2,000 kilogram sahaja.

453
00:25:03,075 --> 00:25:04,576
Sebelum saya berkahwin,

454
00:25:04,743 --> 00:25:08,122
keluarga saya sendiri
boleh buat satu tan kimchi.

455
00:25:08,706 --> 00:25:10,207
Memanglah kerja semakin ringan,

456
00:25:10,290 --> 00:25:13,877
tapi saya risau kimchi tak cukup
untuk sepanjang musim sejuk.

457
00:25:14,002 --> 00:25:16,338
Hei, rendam lama sedikit.

458
00:25:16,588 --> 00:25:17,756
Baiklah.

459
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:19,383
Bagus.

460
00:25:21,552 --> 00:25:24,179
Jadi, ini harinya?

461
00:25:24,763 --> 00:25:26,515
Ya, ini harinya.

462
00:25:29,143 --> 00:25:32,229
Dua bulan. Lama sungguh rasanya.

463
00:25:32,312 --> 00:25:33,939
Ya, memang lama.

464
00:25:34,022 --> 00:25:35,941
Kamu bercakap tentang apa?

465
00:25:36,775 --> 00:25:40,237
Takkanlah kamu dah lupa?

466
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:43,490
Hari ini, Jeong Hyeok
akan pulang daripada bertugas.

467
00:25:43,574 --> 00:25:46,118
Aduhai, saya patut mati!

468
00:25:46,201 --> 00:25:48,579
Saya dah semakin pelupa!

469
00:25:48,662 --> 00:25:50,873
Bukankah kapten lain

470
00:25:50,956 --> 00:25:54,209
bertugas di kota kara juga?

471
00:25:55,169 --> 00:25:58,380
Apa yang istimewanya tentang dia?

472
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:01,925
Sebab dia kacak.

473
00:26:02,551 --> 00:26:04,595
Kita mesti lindungi

474
00:26:04,678 --> 00:26:07,765
aset negara seperti dia.

475
00:26:08,182 --> 00:26:09,182
Oh, begitu.

476
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:13,395
Dah letak kayu api di rumahnya?

477
00:26:13,479 --> 00:26:15,939
Dah letak setimbun. Jangan risau.

478
00:26:17,149 --> 00:26:19,735
Garam, pes soya dan pes cili?

479
00:26:19,818 --> 00:26:22,988
Semua tempayan dah dipenuhkan.

480
00:26:23,113 --> 00:26:27,201
Macam yang awak suruh,
daging diletak di dalam tempayan garam.

481
00:26:37,878 --> 00:26:39,713
Kenapa simpan daging di situ?

482
00:26:39,797 --> 00:26:43,425
Supaya tak mudah rosak.

483
00:26:43,509 --> 00:26:45,511
Hidangan sampingan lain?

484
00:26:45,594 --> 00:26:46,762
Hidangan sampingan?

485
00:26:47,262 --> 00:26:48,680
Mari.

486
00:26:55,854 --> 00:26:57,147
Ini tempat apa?

487
00:26:57,231 --> 00:26:59,149
Awak tak kenal kolong kimchi?

488
00:26:59,233 --> 00:27:01,819
Apa? Mestilah tak.

489
00:27:03,320 --> 00:27:05,322
Ini dipanggil kolong kimchi.

490
00:27:05,405 --> 00:27:07,574
Kimchi dan pes disimpan di sini.

491
00:27:07,658 --> 00:27:11,745
Ia bukan saja tahan lama,
malah, menapai dengan sempurna.

492
00:27:12,746 --> 00:27:15,290
Wah, tempat ini nampak

493
00:27:15,999 --> 00:27:17,751
sangat organik.

494
00:27:17,835 --> 00:27:19,086
Macam mana nak cakap?

495
00:27:19,169 --> 00:27:20,754
Ia sangat "<i>hip</i>".

496
00:27:20,838 --> 00:27:23,882
Jadi, peti sejuk kimchi ini ada

497
00:27:23,966 --> 00:27:25,050
di setiap rumah?

498
00:27:25,551 --> 00:27:26,844
Tak boleh bercakap.

499
00:27:43,652 --> 00:27:45,112
Awak tengok apa?

500
00:27:45,696 --> 00:27:48,657
Di kampung saya,

501
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:51,910
orang masih guna daun dan rumput kering.

502
00:27:52,953 --> 00:27:55,455
Saya tak pernah tengok arang.

503
00:27:56,206 --> 00:27:58,166
Apabila kampung awak sudah moden,

504
00:27:58,250 --> 00:28:00,544
awak pun boleh guna arang, komrad.

505
00:28:02,254 --> 00:28:05,716
Kalau arang dikira moden,
macam mana dengan dapur gas?

506
00:28:09,177 --> 00:28:11,722
Apa? Saya bercakap seorang diri.

507
00:28:12,514 --> 00:28:13,682
Itu pun dilarang?

508
00:28:16,435 --> 00:28:18,937
Jangan terlebih masak.
Biar mentah sedikit.

509
00:28:19,980 --> 00:28:23,025
Saya bercakap seorang diri
tentang kesukaan saya.

510
00:28:35,037 --> 00:28:37,205
Selepas makan, kami mesti bertugas.

511
00:28:37,289 --> 00:28:39,625
Pastikan orang tak nampak awak.

512
00:28:40,959 --> 00:28:42,586
Saya ditinggalkan di sini?

513
00:28:42,669 --> 00:28:45,213
Habis, nak tinggal dengan Kapten Ri?

514
00:28:45,297 --> 00:28:46,297
Bukan.

515
00:28:46,715 --> 00:28:48,508
Bukan itu maksud saya.

516
00:28:48,592 --> 00:28:50,636
Macam mana kalau ada kecemasan?

517
00:28:50,719 --> 00:28:52,679
Kamu tiada telefon bimbit.

518
00:28:53,513 --> 00:28:54,640
Telefon bimbit?

519
00:28:55,849 --> 00:28:57,100
Apa yang dia cakap?

520
00:28:57,661 --> 00:28:58,661
Telefon selular.

521
00:28:58,685 --> 00:29:00,938
Telefon selular?

522
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:03,148
Mestilah ada.

523
00:29:03,231 --> 00:29:05,150
Oh, semua orang ada?

524
00:29:07,671 --> 00:29:08,671
Kami tiada.

525
00:29:08,695 --> 00:29:11,531
Tapi setiap komander kompeni ada.

526
00:29:11,615 --> 00:29:15,827
Ramai orang di negara ini
ada telefon selular.

527
00:29:16,662 --> 00:29:19,081
Kalau dia ada,
bolehlah saya telefon dia.

528
00:29:19,623 --> 00:29:21,663
Telefon selular tak dibenarkan
digunakan dalam unit.

529
00:29:23,627 --> 00:29:25,253
Kalau ada kecemasan?

530
00:29:26,004 --> 00:29:28,757
Tekan lima untuk
pejabat saya di pangkalan.

531
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:31,468
Macam telefon di bilik hotel.

532
00:29:32,511 --> 00:29:33,553
Ini bukan hotel.

533
00:29:33,637 --> 00:29:35,681
Itu contoh.

534
00:29:35,764 --> 00:29:37,766
Saya tak nak dengar contoh.

535
00:29:39,893 --> 00:29:42,729
Baiklah. Kalau ada apa-apa,
saya telefon awak.

536
00:29:42,813 --> 00:29:44,147
Lebih baik jangan.

537
00:29:44,231 --> 00:29:46,817
Saya cuma akan telefon
kalau ada kecemasan.

538
00:29:53,281 --> 00:29:55,242
- Helo…
<i>- Maaf,</i>

539
00:29:55,325 --> 00:29:57,202
<i>puas saya cari cecair mandian.</i>

540
00:29:57,911 --> 00:29:59,413
<i>Tapi tak jumpa.</i>

541
00:29:59,496 --> 00:30:00,831
Guna sabun.

542
00:30:03,458 --> 00:30:04,751
- Helo.
<i>- Ada syampu?</i>

543
00:30:04,835 --> 00:30:06,169
<i>Ini kecemasan.</i>

544
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:07,920
Sabun.

545
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:13,093
<i>Saya cuma nak tanya.</i>

546
00:30:13,176 --> 00:30:15,554
<i>Manalah tahu awak ada, bukan?</i>

547
00:30:15,637 --> 00:30:17,639
<i>Ada lilin beraroma?</i>

548
00:30:18,348 --> 00:30:23,603
<i>Saya perlu guna untuk mandi atau tidur…</i>

549
00:30:27,441 --> 00:30:28,984
<i>Tiada air panas.</i>

550
00:30:29,901 --> 00:30:31,695
<i>Ini masalah besar!</i>

551
00:30:59,681 --> 00:31:01,475
Apa dia suruh buat tadi?

552
00:31:01,975 --> 00:31:03,602
<i>Ada penyepit pada ampaian.</i>

553
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:07,105
Ada penyepit.

554
00:31:07,189 --> 00:31:09,107
<i>Gantung beg mandi.</i>

555
00:31:18,784 --> 00:31:20,035
<i>Selitkan hujung beg</i>

556
00:31:20,118 --> 00:31:22,662
<i>di bawah besen untuk perangkap wap panas.</i>

557
00:31:27,751 --> 00:31:29,961
<i>Kemudian, awak boleh mandi air panas.</i>

558
00:31:31,421 --> 00:31:32,506
Ini…

559
00:31:33,173 --> 00:31:36,635
Macam sauna untuk seorang?

560
00:31:37,552 --> 00:31:38,970
Hebat.

561
00:31:42,224 --> 00:31:43,975
Perlukah saya buat semua ini?

562
00:31:47,437 --> 00:31:50,065
Patutkah saya mandi
beberapa hari lagi saja?

563
00:31:50,816 --> 00:31:55,278
Panas dan selesa.

564
00:31:55,904 --> 00:31:57,697
Leganya.

565
00:32:04,329 --> 00:32:06,414
- Apa lagi?
<i>- Tuan.</i>

566
00:32:07,457 --> 00:32:10,210
<i>Sarjan Master. Ada apa?</i>

567
00:32:10,293 --> 00:32:12,462
<i>Dalam kemalangan pagi ini
di Gunung Suseok,</i>

568
00:32:12,546 --> 00:32:15,674
<i>semua perompak kubur di Pyongyang
turut terbunuh.</i>

569
00:32:16,716 --> 00:32:19,511
JABATAN KESELAMATAN NEGARA

570
00:32:24,182 --> 00:32:25,182
RI JEONG HYEOK

571
00:32:29,855 --> 00:32:32,607
<i>Ini selalu berlaku.
Awak rasa ini kebetulan?</i>

572
00:32:33,108 --> 00:32:37,112
<i>Benarkah Jabatan Keselamatan Negara
ada unit trak rahsia?</i>

573
00:32:38,363 --> 00:32:40,198
BERSAMA MENUJU KEAMANAN KOREA

574
00:32:40,699 --> 00:32:42,659
HANYA YANG TINGGI
DAPAT MELIHAT KEJAHATAN DI BAWAH

575
00:33:13,315 --> 00:33:16,693
Kapten Ri Jeong Hyeok, Komander Kompeni 5.

576
00:33:16,776 --> 00:33:19,404
- Kompeni awak dah tukar pos?
- Sudah, tuan.

577
00:33:19,487 --> 00:33:23,074
Duduklah, minum kopi segera.

578
00:33:29,873 --> 00:33:33,251
Ini kopi dari Selatan.

579
00:33:34,252 --> 00:33:35,253
Tak apa, tuan.

580
00:33:35,337 --> 00:33:38,757
Kenapa? Sebab ini makanan bantuan
dari Korea Selatan?

581
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:41,593
Awalnya, saya pun tak selesa,

582
00:33:42,093 --> 00:33:45,263
tapi rasa pahit manisnya
buat saya ketagih.

583
00:33:47,390 --> 00:33:49,809
Saya rasa awak tak suka benda manis.

584
00:33:51,102 --> 00:33:52,729
Saya mahu laporkan sesuatu.

585
00:33:53,332 --> 00:33:54,332
Laporkan.

586
00:33:54,356 --> 00:33:57,442
Saya dengar sebuah
kenderaan konvoi terbalik pagi ini

587
00:33:57,525 --> 00:33:59,402
dan semua perompak kubur mati.

588
00:34:00,570 --> 00:34:02,781
Saya pun dengar.
Tapi apa boleh buat?

589
00:34:03,865 --> 00:34:05,283
Saya rasa ia perlu disiasat.

590
00:34:05,909 --> 00:34:07,994
Berlanggar dengan kenderaan apa?

591
00:34:08,078 --> 00:34:09,537
Kemalangan atau dirancang?

592
00:34:10,205 --> 00:34:12,624
Kalau dirancang, siapa dalangnya?

593
00:34:13,708 --> 00:34:16,002
Kenapa kejadian ini kerap berlaku?

594
00:34:20,048 --> 00:34:21,925
Banyak soalan awak, kapten,

595
00:34:22,008 --> 00:34:23,468
Izinkan saya siasat.

596
00:34:25,387 --> 00:34:26,721
Baik. Silakan.

597
00:34:27,472 --> 00:34:30,058
Saya akan maklumkan Biro Perbicaraan.

598
00:34:31,393 --> 00:34:33,979
Esok, pergi ke ibu pejabat di Pyongyang.

599
00:34:45,699 --> 00:34:46,700
Awak tak risau?

600
00:34:49,286 --> 00:34:51,204
Pengarah di sana kawan saya.

601
00:34:52,122 --> 00:34:55,583
Kenapa Ri Jeong Hyeok itu angkuh sangat?

602
00:34:55,667 --> 00:34:57,127
Dia kenal orang besar?

603
00:34:57,210 --> 00:35:00,463
Dalam resumenya,
tiada latar belakang keluarga.

604
00:35:00,547 --> 00:35:03,133
Saya masih tak pasti tentang dia.

605
00:35:03,216 --> 00:35:04,216
Ya?

606
00:35:04,718 --> 00:35:06,386
Kolonel Kanan.

607
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:11,433
Saya rasa ada akaun baru.

608
00:35:13,226 --> 00:35:14,436
Siapa pula kali ini?

609
00:35:14,602 --> 00:35:16,646
HOTEL CHILBOSAN

610
00:35:17,564 --> 00:35:20,233
<i>Dia lari setelah menipu satu bilion won.</i>

611
00:35:20,317 --> 00:35:21,943
<i>Dia kini di Shenyang</i>

612
00:35:22,027 --> 00:35:24,821
<i>setelah merentasi Filipina dan Malaysia.</i>

613
00:35:24,904 --> 00:35:26,323
Awak cantik.

614
00:35:26,406 --> 00:35:28,408
<i>Dia seorang hartawan</i>

615
00:35:28,908 --> 00:35:32,662
<i>yang tidak kedekut berbelanja.</i>

616
00:35:32,746 --> 00:35:35,081
<i>Kita patut rapat dengan dia.</i>

617
00:35:35,915 --> 00:35:37,083
Dia dah sampai?

618
00:35:47,719 --> 00:35:48,719
En. Cheon.

619
00:35:51,639 --> 00:35:53,558
- Lama tak jumpa.
- Apa khabar?

620
00:35:54,351 --> 00:35:55,351
Ini…

621
00:36:05,987 --> 00:36:08,948
Kita tak banyak masak,
jadi, ayuh mulakan.

622
00:36:10,992 --> 00:36:13,953
Selepas tandatangan kontrak,
awak akan selamat.

623
00:36:14,037 --> 00:36:16,206
Kami akan lindungi awak

624
00:36:16,289 --> 00:36:18,541
sepanjang proses ke Korea Utara.

625
00:36:18,625 --> 00:36:21,419
Ada pelbagai pakej dengan harga berbeza

626
00:36:21,503 --> 00:36:23,338
serendah 20,000 dolar sebulan.

627
00:36:23,421 --> 00:36:25,965
Saiz rumah, perkhidmatan perubatan,
hiburan,

628
00:36:26,049 --> 00:36:28,176
dan macam-macami lagi perbezaan.

629
00:36:28,259 --> 00:36:30,887
Semuanya berbeza-beza.

630
00:36:31,721 --> 00:36:33,306
Paling mahal berapa?

631
00:36:34,682 --> 00:36:36,142
100,000 dolar sebulan.

632
00:36:36,935 --> 00:36:38,812
1.2 juta dolar setahun.

633
00:36:38,895 --> 00:36:39,895
KAKITANGAN SAH SAHAJA

634
00:36:39,938 --> 00:36:42,315
<i>Rumah dua tingkat dengan bilik resepsi,</i>

635
00:36:42,482 --> 00:36:44,776
<i>sauna tertutup dan kolam renang.</i>

636
00:36:46,569 --> 00:36:48,988
<i>Lengkap dengan lima pengawal peribadi.</i>

637
00:36:50,990 --> 00:36:53,660
<i>Tukang masak, pembantu rumah,</i>

638
00:36:53,743 --> 00:36:56,871
<i>pemandu, tukang kebun juga termasuk.</i>

639
00:36:58,039 --> 00:37:01,793
Awak boleh berhibur dengan golf
atau memburu jika mahu.

640
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:04,003
Awak juga boleh memasuki kasino.

641
00:37:04,087 --> 00:37:05,713
Apa pendapat awak?

642
00:37:06,965 --> 00:37:10,969
Saya akan bayar 200,000 dolar sebulan,
2.4 juta dolar setahun.

643
00:37:12,929 --> 00:37:17,225
Tapi pastikan awak tak ubah fikiran
setelah saya masuk ke sana.

644
00:37:17,308 --> 00:37:21,813
Ingat, semua wang saya disimpan
di dalam akaun luar pesisir.

645
00:37:22,313 --> 00:37:24,524
Jika rambut saya disentuh sekalipun,

646
00:37:25,191 --> 00:37:29,070
awak takkan dapat bayaran, faham?

647
00:37:29,904 --> 00:37:30,905
En. Gu Seung-jun.

648
00:37:31,781 --> 00:37:34,200
Undang-undang had untuk serangan
ialah lima tahun.

649
00:37:34,284 --> 00:37:35,994
Tujuh tahun untuk mencederakan.

650
00:37:36,077 --> 00:37:38,663
Sepuluh tahun
untuk kes penipuan macam awak.

651
00:37:38,746 --> 00:37:42,876
Ramai rakyat Korea Selatan
habiskan tempoh had di sini

652
00:37:42,959 --> 00:37:45,545
di bawah perlindungan orang saya

653
00:37:45,628 --> 00:37:48,423
untuk mengelak polis Korea Selatan
dan Interpol.

654
00:37:49,048 --> 00:37:50,925
Saya tahu.

655
00:37:51,426 --> 00:37:53,344
Sebab itu saya di sini.

656
00:37:53,428 --> 00:37:55,805
Kami gadaikan nyawa dalam bisnes ini.

657
00:37:55,889 --> 00:37:59,517
Demi melindungi pelanggan
yang telah berbuat jenayah,

658
00:37:59,601 --> 00:38:01,728
kami juga membuat jenayah.

659
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:07,275
Jadi, tanpa kepercayaan dua hala,
kita tak boleh teruskan.

660
00:38:07,984 --> 00:38:12,155
Ya, saya faham.
Kenapa serius sangat?

661
00:38:13,281 --> 00:38:14,365
Aduhai.

662
00:38:14,449 --> 00:38:18,077
Datang ke Korea Utara
hanya untuk duduk di Gunung Kumgang.

663
00:38:18,161 --> 00:38:20,622
GU SEUNG-JUN

664
00:38:20,705 --> 00:38:22,749
Satu, dua, tiga.

665
00:38:23,208 --> 00:38:24,542
Empat, lima, enam.

666
00:38:25,084 --> 00:38:26,920
- Tujuh, lapan, sembilan.
- Hei.

667
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:28,463
Nam Sik.

668
00:38:29,172 --> 00:38:31,716
Kenapa masih di sini?
Dah pukul berapa?

669
00:38:31,841 --> 00:38:32,717
- Balik.
- Mak.

670
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,219
- Mak!
- Jom.

671
00:38:34,302 --> 00:38:36,554
- Mari sini.
- Puas mak panggil.

672
00:38:36,638 --> 00:38:38,806
- Lekas, mak kamu panggil.
- Balik.

673
00:38:48,358 --> 00:38:49,567
Ayah!

674
00:38:50,944 --> 00:38:51,944
Ayah!

675
00:38:53,154 --> 00:38:54,155
Ya.

676
00:38:56,491 --> 00:38:58,076
Kenapa kamu sendirian?

677
00:38:58,159 --> 00:38:59,159
Ini apa?

678
00:39:01,329 --> 00:39:02,329
Kegemaran kamu.

679
00:39:02,372 --> 00:39:03,623
Donat.

680
00:39:06,125 --> 00:39:07,377
- Mari.
- Ya.

681
00:39:19,138 --> 00:39:20,138
Apa?

682
00:39:21,391 --> 00:39:23,351
Kejutan apa pula kali ini?

683
00:39:26,563 --> 00:39:28,606
Sayang, elektrik dah tiada.

684
00:39:28,690 --> 00:39:30,483
Tolong pasang pelita, ya?

685
00:39:42,829 --> 00:39:44,038
Mari makan.

686
00:39:48,876 --> 00:39:50,169
Apa pula kali ini?

687
00:39:51,087 --> 00:39:53,381
Apa muslihat mereka?

688
00:40:02,515 --> 00:40:05,643
Saya dah agak. Dia takkan jawab.

689
00:40:07,478 --> 00:40:09,939
Mereka nak tanam saya?

690
00:40:18,656 --> 00:40:19,866
Di mana lampu picit?

691
00:41:16,297 --> 00:41:17,548
Apa awak buat?

692
00:41:20,426 --> 00:41:22,053
Kenapa awak balik?

693
00:41:22,136 --> 00:41:23,471
Awak kata nak lilin.

694
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:33,356
Awak perlukan lilin untuk mandi
dan tidur.

695
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:36,067
Itu lilin biasa.

696
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:42,115
Saya nak lilin aromaterapi.

697
00:41:55,002 --> 00:41:56,629
Saya minta maaf.

698
00:41:58,756 --> 00:42:00,967
Saya buat awak serba salah.

699
00:42:01,384 --> 00:42:03,553
Tapi saya tak sangka

700
00:42:04,387 --> 00:42:06,597
akan lalui semua ini.

701
00:42:21,237 --> 00:42:24,866
BERDIKARI

702
00:42:55,897 --> 00:42:58,483
Cepatlah sedikit.

703
00:43:00,651 --> 00:43:03,488
Macam mana kalau orang tahu?

704
00:43:09,494 --> 00:43:11,579
Wah, terangnya.

705
00:43:12,663 --> 00:43:15,124
Ho Yeong, dah boleh buat kerja rumah?

706
00:43:15,208 --> 00:43:18,753
Mak, kalau dah tiada elektrik,
bolehlah saya tidur.

707
00:43:20,546 --> 00:43:21,798
Budak bertuah.

708
00:43:22,256 --> 00:43:26,052
Ayah kamu curi-curi bawa bateri
untuk kamu buat kerja rumah.

709
00:43:26,636 --> 00:43:28,429
Kalau dapat nombor corot lagi,

710
00:43:28,513 --> 00:43:33,059
mak akan bogelkan kamu
dan halau dari rumah ini.

711
00:43:33,142 --> 00:43:34,852
Saya bukan yang tercorot.

