00:43:34,936 --> 00:43:36,437
Namsik di belakang saya.

713
00:43:36,521 --> 00:43:37,521
Ya?

714
00:43:37,855 --> 00:43:40,566
Kamu bangga Nam Sik di belakang kamu?

715
00:43:41,859 --> 00:43:42,859
Siapkan.

716
