00:44:07,927 --> 00:44:09,554
Saya sentiasa cuba.

725
00:44:09,637 --> 00:44:11,848
Kenapa awak cakap begitu?

726
00:44:11,931 --> 00:44:13,891
Isteri Kapten Na.

727
00:44:13,975 --> 00:44:17,061
Saya nampak dia bawa barang
ke rumah kolonel kanan.

728
00:44:17,144 --> 00:44:18,144
Apa?

729
00:44:24,819 --> 00:44:26,904
Cik Ma, awak di dalam?

730
00:44:31,617 --> 00:44:32,827
Cik Ma.

731
00:44:33,661 --> 00:44:34,912
Awak datang?

732
00:44:35,705 --> 00:44:37,456
Tengok Ok Geum.

733
00:44:37,540 --> 00:44:41,043
Dia jana generator
supaya saya boleh tonton televisyen.

734
00:44:42,086 --> 00:44:44,672
Ok Geum, kaki awak okey?

735
00:44:44,755 --> 00:44:45,882
Okey.

736
00:44:46,048 --> 00:44:48,885
Asalkan dapat tengok awak ketawa

737
00:44:48,968 --> 00:44:50,219
saya rela patah kaki.

738
00:44:50,303 --> 00:44:53,431
Tiada masalah.

739
00:45:06,402 --> 00:45:07,402
Sang-a.

740
00:45:11,449 --> 00:45:13,951
Saya makan banyak tadi.

741
00:45:14,035 --> 00:45:15,453
Buncit dibuatnya.

742
00:45:15,536 --> 00:45:16,536
Ya?

743
00:45:17,330 --> 00:45:19,582
Ada berita baru?

744
00:45:19,665 --> 00:45:22,293
Kalau ada berita baru,
orang akan telefon.

745
00:45:22,376 --> 00:45:23,961
Kasihan. Dia masih muda.

746
00:45:24,045 --> 00:45:25,671
Belum berkahwin pun.

747
00:45:26,255 --> 00:45:27,381
Ayah pula

748
00:45:27,465 --> 00:45:30,927
kata nak wariskan perniagaan kepadanya.

749
00:45:31,010 --> 00:45:32,386
Tentu dia dah berharap.

750
00:45:32,470 --> 00:45:33,888
Malang tak berbau..

751
00:45:34,430 --> 00:45:35,723
Apa maksud awak?

752
00:45:35,806 --> 00:45:38,392
Kita semua tahu ayah tak serius pun.

753
00:45:38,476 --> 00:45:40,102
Ayah takkan buat begitu.

754
00:45:40,186 --> 00:45:41,187
Buat apa?

755
00:45:41,270 --> 00:45:42,980
Dia cuma nak acah suami saya.

756
00:45:43,064 --> 00:45:45,149
Pewaris tetap anak lelaki sulung.

757
00:45:45,232 --> 00:45:49,111
Dia nak suami saya tingkatkan usaha.

758
00:45:49,195 --> 00:45:52,114
Jadi, dia kata nak wariskan
kepada anak perempuan.

759
00:45:52,573 --> 00:45:54,450
Licik sungguh.

760
00:45:57,787 --> 00:46:03,125
Saham Seri's Choice kekal kukuh
tiga hari berturut-turut.

761
00:46:03,209 --> 00:46:04,543
Jenama Seri's Choice…

762
00:46:04,627 --> 00:46:07,296
Apabila berita
tentang CEO mereka tersebar,

763
00:46:07,380 --> 00:46:09,215
harga saham akan menjunam.

764
00:46:09,298 --> 00:46:11,384
Pelabur tempatan…

765
00:46:11,467 --> 00:46:13,260
<i>Awak tahu tentang saham?</i>

766
00:46:14,804 --> 00:46:16,305
Tentu awak tak tahu,

767
00:46:16,806 --> 00:46:18,849
Harga saham berubah-ubah

768
00:46:18,933 --> 00:46:22,895
hingga berbilion won hari demi hari.

769
00:46:24,689 --> 00:46:27,149
Dulu, saya labur tiga bilion kepada kawan

770
00:46:27,233 --> 00:46:28,693
tapi rugi semuanya.

771
00:46:37,410 --> 00:46:39,036
Tapi…

772
00:46:40,162 --> 00:46:42,707
Saya tak sesedih sekarang.

773
00:46:43,791 --> 00:46:46,168
Saya lebih sedih sekarang

774
00:46:47,044 --> 00:46:49,630
berbanding kerugian tiga bilion won.

775
00:46:51,340 --> 00:46:53,050
Apa saya buat di sini?

776
00:46:53,634 --> 00:46:57,179
Saya tak nak tahu pun lokasi Korea Utara.

777
00:46:57,763 --> 00:47:00,558
Lagipun, kenapa saya menangis

778
00:47:00,641 --> 00:47:02,435
di depan orang tak dikenali?

779
00:47:03,144 --> 00:47:04,770
Sedihnya.

780
00:47:12,028 --> 00:47:14,530
Jangan risau. Saya dah tak nampak.

781
00:47:17,408 --> 00:47:20,369
Tuah dan malang
ibarat tali yang saling terjalin.

782
00:47:21,245 --> 00:47:23,622
Semuanya akan baik-baik saja.

783
00:47:25,249 --> 00:47:26,375
Awak pasti?

784
00:47:27,501 --> 00:47:28,544
Saya pasti.

785
00:47:34,258 --> 00:47:35,676
Awak nak ke mana?

786
00:47:36,302 --> 00:47:38,304
Pagi esok, saya ke Pyongyang.

787
00:47:38,888 --> 00:47:39,888
Pyongyang?

788
00:47:40,973 --> 00:47:42,141
Bila awak balik?

789
00:47:43,476 --> 00:47:44,477
Saya tak tahu.

790
00:47:45,352 --> 00:47:47,438
Saya mungkin tak dapat hantar awak.

791
00:47:47,938 --> 00:47:50,691
Tapi kawan-kawan saya akan tolong.

792
00:47:51,776 --> 00:47:54,111
Saya beli barang yang awak cari.

793
00:48:06,123 --> 00:48:07,123
Tunggu.

794
00:48:10,419 --> 00:48:12,379
Siapa nama awak?

795
00:48:14,340 --> 00:48:17,426
Saya nak ingat untuk balas budi awak.

796
00:48:18,427 --> 00:48:20,763
Tak perlu. Ini bukannya budi.

797
00:48:23,224 --> 00:48:24,224
Ingat.

798
00:48:24,600 --> 00:48:27,436
Jangan beritahu sesiapa
tentang kejadian di sini.

799
00:48:28,562 --> 00:48:30,397
Kalau awak lupakan, lebih baik.

800
00:48:56,298 --> 00:48:57,716
Apa semua ini?

801
00:49:01,846 --> 00:49:03,305
Apa ini?

802
00:49:04,849 --> 00:49:08,978
Bukankah dia suruh guna sabun saja?

803
00:49:10,187 --> 00:49:11,981
Semua ini dari Korea Selatan.

804
00:49:31,458 --> 00:49:33,419
Dari mana dia dapat?

805
00:49:39,008 --> 00:49:40,426
Cari kosmetik?

806
00:49:44,263 --> 00:49:45,263
Dari Korea Selatan.

807
00:49:45,764 --> 00:49:47,808
Penyegar, krim pembersih,

808
00:49:47,892 --> 00:49:50,060
krim siang dan krim malam.

809
00:49:50,603 --> 00:49:51,604
Nak yang mana?

810
00:49:52,354 --> 00:49:53,480
Semua.

811
00:50:02,948 --> 00:50:03,949
Oh, Tuhan.

812
00:50:04,617 --> 00:50:05,910
Nak pakaian dalam?

813
00:50:06,744 --> 00:50:08,162
Ini pun dari Selatan.

814
00:50:09,038 --> 00:50:13,334
Ini Vivian, ini Venus.
Itu Bodyguard.

815
00:50:13,417 --> 00:50:14,668
Nak yang mana?

816
00:50:14,752 --> 00:50:17,087
Semua juga.

817
00:50:17,838 --> 00:50:21,467
Awak nak saiz apa?

818
00:50:26,513 --> 00:50:27,514
Mana-manalah.

819
00:50:31,018 --> 00:50:34,563
Dia fikir saya sebesar ini?

820
00:50:34,647 --> 00:50:35,981
Mungkin muat.

821
00:50:42,821 --> 00:50:45,658
DISINFEKTAN

822
00:50:47,952 --> 00:50:48,952
Sudahlah.

823
00:50:50,746 --> 00:50:52,831
Berlagak tak peduli, tapi prihatin.

824
00:51:09,056 --> 00:51:10,266
Kalau ini mimpi,

825
00:51:11,642 --> 00:51:13,811
cepatlah terjaga.

826
00:51:29,576 --> 00:51:33,831
Tilam lateks ini sangat empuk dan selesa.

827
00:51:36,000 --> 00:51:37,918
Ini katil saya.

828
00:52:03,527 --> 00:52:07,531
Saya dah agak. Itu cuma mimpi.

829
00:52:08,198 --> 00:52:10,826
Saya tahu ia tak benar.

830
00:52:10,909 --> 00:52:12,536
Korea Utara?

831
00:52:12,619 --> 00:52:15,205
Dahsyatnya mimpi semalam!

832
00:52:25,632 --> 00:52:29,011
Kenapa ada gambar mereka?

833
00:52:30,554 --> 00:52:32,139
Saya tak letak di situ.

834
00:52:32,222 --> 00:52:35,726
Tak, ini bukan mimpi.

835
00:52:35,809 --> 00:52:37,353
Mimpi saya dah berakhir.

836
00:52:37,436 --> 00:52:39,104
Ini bukan mimpi.

837
00:52:39,188 --> 00:52:41,273
Jangan bangun. Jangan.

838
00:52:41,357 --> 00:52:43,359
<i>Jangan bangun. Tak nak bangun!</i>

839
00:52:50,074 --> 00:52:52,659
<i>Di manakah kita?
Kita di pekan</i>

840
00:52:52,993 --> 00:52:56,372
<i>Ke manakah kita?
Ke sekolah</i>

841
00:52:56,538 --> 00:52:58,749
<i>Apa tujuannya?
Menimba ilmu</i>

842
00:52:58,832 --> 00:53:01,085
<i>Bersama siapa?</i>

843
00:53:13,472 --> 00:53:14,472
PETA

844
00:53:22,898 --> 00:53:24,775
DENGAN JIWA DAN SEMANGAT GUNUNG BAEKDU

845
00:53:35,035 --> 00:53:39,540
PARTI PEKERJA KOREA

846
00:53:39,623 --> 00:53:41,667
PEMBANTU

847
00:53:54,930 --> 00:53:56,014
Cepatlah.

848
00:53:59,351 --> 00:54:01,270
Ikut sini.

849
00:54:02,813 --> 00:54:04,022
Kad pengenalan.

850
00:54:08,402 --> 00:54:10,946
RI JEONG HYEOK

851
00:54:12,906 --> 00:54:16,034
Awak Kapten Ri Jeong Hyeok
dari Batalion Polis Awam?

852
00:54:16,118 --> 00:54:17,118
Ya.

853
00:54:17,995 --> 00:54:19,121
Dia di sini.

854
00:54:22,708 --> 00:54:25,085
Kami dari
Bahagian Siasatan Biro Perbicaraan.

855
00:54:25,169 --> 00:54:26,837
Saya memang ingin ke sana.

856
00:54:26,920 --> 00:54:28,213
Saya ingin siasat satu kes.

857
00:54:28,297 --> 00:54:32,134
Ri Jeong Hyeok. Awak yang akan disiasat.

858
00:54:32,718 --> 00:54:33,719
Ikut kami.

859
00:54:42,144 --> 00:54:43,520
KEDAULATAN DAN KEMAKMURAN

860
00:54:51,153 --> 00:54:53,363
Tentu awak tak pernah
ke tempat seperti ini.

861
00:54:54,740 --> 00:54:57,367
Maaf, tiada tempat kerusi lain.

862
00:54:58,702 --> 00:54:59,702
Silakan duduk.

863
00:55:08,045 --> 00:55:11,757
Kita berbual dulu, boleh?

864
00:55:15,552 --> 00:55:16,553
Silakan.

865
00:55:17,763 --> 00:55:22,184
Khabarnya,
awak hina rakyat yang bekerja keras

866
00:55:22,267 --> 00:55:24,937
di depan askar Korea Selatan.

867
00:55:25,020 --> 00:55:28,148
Mereka rentas sempadan untuk rompak kubur.

868
00:55:28,232 --> 00:55:30,317
Bagi awak itu pekerjaan mulia?

869
00:55:30,609 --> 00:55:32,027
Itu pendapat awak? Baik.

870
00:55:33,028 --> 00:55:34,655
Mana artifak itu?

871
00:55:34,738 --> 00:55:37,157
Semua perompak kubur itu dah mati.

872
00:55:38,033 --> 00:55:39,535
Kita takkan tahu.

873
00:55:40,536 --> 00:55:43,413
Leftenan Komander Cho Cheol Gang
dari Jabatan Keselamatan Negara

874
00:55:43,497 --> 00:55:46,917
boleh siasat sendiri kes ini.

875
00:55:47,000 --> 00:55:50,879
Tapi awak bertegas hendak
bawa kes ini ke Pyongyang

876
00:55:50,963 --> 00:55:53,882
manakala perompak mati
dengan mencurigakan.

877
00:55:53,966 --> 00:55:57,010
Tentulah kami syak awak.

878
00:55:57,970 --> 00:56:00,556
Logiknya, pengeluar permit
tak boleh siasat kes sendiri.

879
00:56:01,848 --> 00:56:04,017
Awak tak guna logik akal?

880
00:56:05,913 --> 00:56:06,913
"Logik akal"?

881
00:56:06,937 --> 00:56:09,064
Jangan buat tuduhan melulu.

882
00:56:09,147 --> 00:56:10,147
Ada bukti?

883
00:56:12,150 --> 00:56:13,318
Dengar sini.

884
00:56:14,111 --> 00:56:16,572
Adakah paku perlukan dinding
yang sudah berlubang?

885
00:56:17,781 --> 00:56:19,908
Kita guna tukul
untuk benamkan ia ke dinding.

886
00:56:19,992 --> 00:56:21,660
Di sinilah tempat kami menukul paku.

887
00:56:21,743 --> 00:56:25,539
Kami tak perlukan bukti.
Kami boleh reka kes jenayah untuk awak.

888
00:56:25,622 --> 00:56:26,623
Faham?

889
00:56:27,393 --> 00:56:28,393
Ya?

890
00:56:28,417 --> 00:56:30,961
Nahaslah awak kerana bercakap begitu.

891
00:56:31,878 --> 00:56:32,963
Tak guna!

892
00:56:33,755 --> 00:56:36,800
Siapa yang buat hal sampai
diheret ke sini?

893
00:56:36,883 --> 00:56:38,427
Apa awak kata?

894
00:56:38,510 --> 00:56:40,387
Ulang balik kalau berani!

895
00:56:42,180 --> 00:56:43,807
Siapa lelaki itu?

896
00:56:45,267 --> 00:56:46,267
Hei!

897
00:56:48,645 --> 00:56:51,064
Jeneral, kenapa awak ke sini…

898
00:56:52,357 --> 00:56:53,734
Awak dah gila?

899
00:56:53,817 --> 00:56:55,027
Dah hilang akal?

900
00:56:55,110 --> 00:56:56,110
Tak…

901
00:56:57,279 --> 00:57:00,073
Jeong Hyeok, awak tak apa-apa?

902
00:57:00,157 --> 00:57:01,366
Saya tak apa-apa.

903
00:57:03,869 --> 00:57:06,288
Tunggu apa lagi?
Bawa dia ke pejabat saya.

904
00:57:09,875 --> 00:57:12,210
Jeneral, siapa dia…

905
00:57:13,462 --> 00:57:15,213
Nahaslah awak, bodoh.

906
00:57:15,797 --> 00:57:18,884
Dia anak tunggal Pengarah Biro Politik Am.

907
00:57:19,551 --> 00:57:20,551
Apa?

908
00:57:22,220 --> 00:57:23,220
Tuhan.

909
00:57:44,117 --> 00:57:45,994
- Helo.
<i>- Cho Cheol Gang!</i>

910
00:57:46,078 --> 00:57:48,246
<i>Awak sengaja nak musnahkan</i>

911
00:57:48,705 --> 00:57:50,874
<i>- kerjaya saya?</i>
- Kenapa?

912
00:57:50,957 --> 00:57:55,295
Awak tahu siapa ayah
Kapten Ri Jeong Hyeok?

913
00:57:55,379 --> 00:57:57,798
<i>Saya tak tahu. Latar belakangnya kosong.</i>

914
00:57:57,881 --> 00:57:59,591
Awak rasa kenapa ia kosong?

915
00:57:59,675 --> 00:58:01,718
Sebab keluarganya berpengaruh!

916
00:58:01,802 --> 00:58:03,804
Apa awak cakap?

917
00:58:03,887 --> 00:58:06,765
Jangan pengsan.

918
00:58:06,848 --> 00:58:09,518
Ri Jeong Hyeok…

919
00:58:10,435 --> 00:58:12,312
Anak Pengarah Biro Politik Am.

920
00:58:12,771 --> 00:58:15,148
Apa awak kata?

921
00:58:15,232 --> 00:58:18,694
<i>Ya, sekali dengar,
macam tak boleh hadam, bukan?</i>

922
00:58:19,194 --> 00:58:21,029
<i>Dia anak Pengarah Biro Politik Am.</i>

923
00:58:21,697 --> 00:58:23,865
<i>Pengarah itu ada dua anak lelaki.</i>

924
00:58:23,949 --> 00:58:27,244
<i>Tetapi seorang dah mati dalam kemalangan.</i>

925
00:58:27,327 --> 00:58:28,161
Awak pasti?

926
00:58:28,245 --> 00:58:30,622
<i>Saya harap saya silap!</i>

927
00:58:31,331 --> 00:58:33,750
<i>Apa awak nak buat?</i>

928
00:58:33,834 --> 00:58:34,960
Saya telefon awak esok.

929
00:58:35,043 --> 00:58:38,255
<i>Itu pun kalau saya masih ada di pejabat.</i>

930
00:58:38,714 --> 00:58:40,257
<i>Kenapalah saya…</i>

931
00:58:46,930 --> 00:58:47,930
<i>Ini adik saya.</i>

932
00:58:48,849 --> 00:58:50,726
<i>Ini kawan abang.</i>

933
00:58:57,190 --> 00:58:59,568
Jadi, adik Mu Hyeok

934
00:59:01,027 --> 00:59:02,487
ialah Ri Jeong Hyeok?

935
00:59:09,786 --> 00:59:12,205
Akhirnya, Dae-gil hidup atau mati?

936
00:59:17,794 --> 00:59:22,007
Cakaplah. Saya cuma tonton
<i>The Slave Hunters</i> hingga episod 14.

937
00:59:23,800 --> 00:59:25,719
Apa berlaku kepada Dae-gil?

938
00:59:27,179 --> 00:59:28,179
Dae-gil…

939
00:59:29,890 --> 00:59:31,016
Mati.

940
00:59:31,099 --> 00:59:33,310
Aduhai. Betulkah?

941
00:59:34,519 --> 00:59:37,564
Tak sangka Dae-gil akhirnya mati.

942
00:59:37,647 --> 00:59:41,693
Itu drama sepuluh tahun lalu.

943
00:59:42,694 --> 00:59:44,070
Awak datang untuk berbual?

944
00:59:44,154 --> 00:59:46,156
Maaf.

945
00:59:47,491 --> 00:59:49,159
Gwang Beom. Eun Dong.

946
00:59:49,242 --> 00:59:50,827
- Makan dulu.
- Ya.

947
00:59:50,911 --> 00:59:53,872
Kenapa kamu semua menggali?

948
00:59:53,955 --> 00:59:55,207
Awak rasa?

949
00:59:55,373 --> 00:59:58,794
Untuk tanam perempuan Korea Selatan
yang biadab ini.

950
01:00:00,337 --> 01:00:02,589
Kami gali sumber air bawah tanah.

951
01:00:03,298 --> 01:00:05,592
Kapten Ri suruh kami lindungi awak.

952
01:00:05,675 --> 01:00:08,762
Kami perlukan alasan
untuk bawa awak keluar.

953
01:00:09,930 --> 01:00:13,391
Itu yang kapten kamu suruh?

954
01:00:13,934 --> 01:00:15,268
Dia suruh kamu lindungi saya?

955
